description: Try our easy to follow Spanish Seafood Stew recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Spanish Seafood Stew Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 270g garlic bread, cooked according to packet instructions (to serve)
0.5 cup flat-leaf parsley leaves, roughly chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.

Add onion, garlic and celery and cook, stirring often, for 4 minutes or until tender. Add orange rind, 1/4 cup orange juice, tomatoes, wine and 3/4 cup water. Stir until well combined and mixture comes to the boil.

Add marinara mix and fish. Reduce heat to low and simmer, stirring occasionally, for 20 minutes or until fish is tender. Add mussels and olives to pan and cover. Cook for a further 5-8 minutes or until mussels open. Remove from heat. Stir through parsley.
